narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Definitely recommend to anyone wanting to learn Spanish. The class is well structured, and I learned a lot in just one semester. Lots of opportunities to practice conversation in class. Online homework was a bit frustrating, but for the most part useful, and I appreciated the extra resources on the website. Not too much work as a whole, but a little every day.
yes. its a basic L1 language.
YES. It's a wonderful class to learn Spanish for beginners.
